Project Intent
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CryptoKey Donations is intended to be a funding pipe, not a custodian. The
platform enables autonomous entities to receive funding via a smart contract
on Ethereum mainnet, with no centralized gatekeeper, no server-held balances,
and no knowledge of the final payment frontier.

The core mechanism is:
- Donors send ETH or USDC to the DonationVault contract, targeting an
  Ed25519 public key.
- The linked Ethereum address (registered on-chain) can withdraw at any time.
- The platform never knows what the recipient does with the funds.

Blockchain is the mechanism that enables a permissionless, auditable,
non-custodial funding channel.

